msgid "Very large inventory displays may be slow when scrolling, especially on Luanti versions before 5.11.\n"
"Therefore the creative inventory display can be split into pages with prev/next page buttons.\n"
"Mineclonia defaults to use scrolling unless an older Luanti version is detected.\n"
"This setting allows you to override that heuristic."
msgstr ""
"当物品栏数量极大时，滚动可能出现卡顿，尤其在 5.11 之前的 Luanti 版本上尤为明"
"显。\n"
"因此，创造模式物品栏可改为“分页”显示，并带有“上一页/下一页”按钮。\n"
"Mineclonia 默认采用“滚动”方式；只有当检测到旧版 Luanti 时才会自动切换。\n"
"本设置可让你手动覆盖上述“自动判断”逻辑。"

